column5: Don't know if there is any good bass,musky or pickerel fishing left since I hardly go out after Thanksgiving. I fished for pickerel at night from shore right up to closer but thats about it. If anyone has room in their boat and needs a good net man. Send me a message. I'm available all days except Sunday(poker day).  If not, I'll go check out a few shore spots and report back, since the girls dont want to rent a boat out in the cold.
Gezz Johnny, the fishin just starts gettin good now.
The muskies and pickerel are surely on for awhile still. Enjoy your reports, you should hook up no doubt and get out there. Cheers.
Man that would really make my day but there is a reason I dont go out after Thanksgiving. I hate the cold! And I assume its even colder up there!
Hey Johnny,  I hear the hot Muskie bait this time of year is a human thumb REPLICA.  Try not to confuse that this time
I'm working on the patent right now.
